node.text: We are turning into the laughing stock of the world. This is the kind of mess you’d see in a slapstick d-rated airplane flick. Yet it’s happening in the White House! I don’t think this guy is an actual intern, but the WH allowed him to go in and make this video…

node.title: I thought this was a joke! It’s real!!!

node.text: The enemy aims to steal, kill and destroy. He does this by targeting your identity and by causing you to doubt who God has created you to be. Now more than ever we need to remember who we are and Who’s we are. We are called, set apart, and chosen for such a time as this. Let’s stand up!! #StandUp #Believers
